被宽容，普通想法易被赞许为美妙创意\n2. 这种反馈混淆并非因不聪明或不努力，而是从未需要依赖聪明努力获取资源","type":1}]},{"desc":"白月光的破灭","timestamp":150000,"detail":"","points":[{"desc":"・白月光的破灭源于对娇艳衰败的本能厌恶","detail":"1. 娇艳花朵因自身价值被放进温室呵护，但娇艳会随时间褪色、花朵会枯萎，人们会对衰败的花朵产生厌恶、不安与反感\n2. 白月光的美好是自我高估的结果，带着期许滤镜回望会发现是对对方的误读","type":1},{"desc":"・温室花朵的困境源于环境与规则的变化","detail":"1. 温室是他人搭建的，娇艳是时间清算的，温室最终会被拆除\n2. 长大后情绪化没人哄、能力不足没人兜，需站在真实交换的社会位置，价格透明后社会会变得刻薄","type":1}]},{"desc":"结语","timestamp":194000,"detail":"","points":[]}],"chapter_recommend_type":1,"chapter_abstract":"年轻女性往往因美貌享有特权，如更多关注、耐心和宽容。然而，随着年龄增长，美貌不再是优势，人们开始关注真实的能力。这种变化导致女性对自我产生怀疑，白月光破灭。只有聪明的人才能将美貌红利转化为人生本金。","chapter_recommend_source":2,"push_scene":[],"chapter_bar_color":null},"ad_charge_passive_unlock_config":{"trial_btn_config":{"btn_show_second":3,"btn_text":"秒后解锁本集","btn_show_frequency":1,"show_second_type":2},"broadcast_btn_config":{"btn_show_second":5,"btn_text":"秒后解锁下一集","btn_show_frequency":1,"show_second_type":2}},"common_button":{"button_list":[{"basic_info":{"btn_name":"playlet_iaa_next","exemptions":[1,2],"btn_type":"entertainment","btn_ui_style":0,"buttons":[{"content":{"content":""},"click_action":{"click_action":1,"btn_data_Keys":null,"behavior_type":0},"btn_data_keys":null}],"btn_datas":null},"priority":200400}]},"trends_infos":null,"chapter_bar_color":null},{"aweme_id":"7604405687271181604","desc":"为什么优秀的上位者那么少？ #性  #欲望","create_time":1770704400,"author":{"uid":"3749764821694632","card_entries_not_display":null,"nickname":"狐狸的观念","personal_tag_list":null,"can_set_geofencing":null,"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/aweme-avatar/tos-cn-i-0813_owCnIA2ADGjAQeeglS3AhVCbhvY9CkA34IAnsX","url_list":["https://p3-pc.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/aweme-avatar/tos-cn-i-0813_owCnIA2ADGjAQeeglS3AhVCbhvY9CkA34IAnsX.jpeg?from=327834062"],"width":720,"height":720},"creator_tag_list":null,"risk_notice_text":"","follow_status":1,"data_label_list":null,"story25_comment":0,"not_seen_item_id_list_v2":null,"custom_verify":"","ban_user_functions":null,"cf_list":null,"interest_tags":nul